Anarchic Bombs*				KEY:Discovery ~ Anarchic Bombs									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery																																																																															PREVARGTEQ:classlevel("Alchemist"),6												DESC:When the alchemist creates a bomb, he can choose to have it deal chaotic divine damage. Lawful creatures that take a direct hit from an anarchic bomb must succeed at a Fortitude save (DC = %1) or be staggered on their next turn. Against neutral creatures, anarchic bombs deal half damage, and such targets are not affected by their staggering effect. Anarchic bombs have no effect on chaotic-aligned creatures.|AlchemistBombDC																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.20
