Diminished Spellcasting			KEY:Survivor ~ Diminished Spellcasting								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClericClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																	DESC:A survivor's number of spells per day for each spell level is one less than normal (for example, a 4th-level survivor can cast three cantrips, two 2nd-level spells, and one 1st-level spell per day). If this reduces the number of spells for a level to 0, she gains only the bonus spells for that level she would be entitled to based on her Wisdom score.																																																																																																																																																																																																																	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=0|-1	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=1|-1	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=2|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,3	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=3|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,5	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=4|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,7	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=5|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,9	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=6|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,11	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=7|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,13	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=8|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,15	BONUS:SPELLCAST|CLASS=Druid;LEVEL=9|-1|PREVARGTEQ:DruidLVL,17																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.24
