# Envoy of Balance Abilities
# ==============================

Incisive Spells				KEY:Envoy of Balance ~ Incisive Spells								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.EoBClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																													DESC:An envoy of balance gains a +1 bonus on caster level checks to overcome the spell resistance of creatures with an alignment subtype. This bonus increases to +2 at 9th level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.30
Endowment					KEY:Envoy of Balance ~ Endowment									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.EoBClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																		DEFINE:EoBEndowmentLVL|0	DEFINE:EoBEndowmentCount|0		DESC:At 2nd level and again at 4th, 6th, and 8th level, an envoy of balance gains one of the available endowments.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Envoy of Balance Endowment|min(3,(EoBEndowmentLVL/2))																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.30	BONUS:VAR|EoBEndowmentCount|1+(EnvoyOfBalanceLVL>=4)+(EnvoyOfBalanceLVL>=6)
Contravening Armament			KEY:Envoy of Balance ~ Contravening Armament							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.EoBClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																													DESC:An envoy of balance's natural and manufactured weapons bypass alignment-based damage reduction. As a standard action, she can touch an ally to transfer this ability to him for 1 minute, during which time the envoy of balance can't benefit from the ability. The envoy of balance can transfer this ability a number oftimes per day equal to 1/2 her class level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.31
Ethical Paradox				KEY:Envoy of Balance ~ Ethical Paradox								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.EoBClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																													DESC:An envoy of balance remains unaffected by effects from spells and magical abilities based on her alignment or faith. She doesn't trigger glyphs, symbols, magical traps, or magical sensors set to activate based on a creature's alignment or religion. She counts as the most favorable alignment or faith for the purposes of any harmful effects these alignment- or faith-based spells or abilities may have, but doesn't gain benefits these effects might grant those of a particular alignment or faith unless she is actually of that alignment or faith.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.31
Retributive Symmetry			KEY:Envoy of Balance ~ Retributive Symmetry							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.EoBClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																													DESC:Once per day as an immediate action, an envoy of balance can cause a spell targeting her to affect both herself and the spell's caster at full effect, as if both creatures had spell turning cast on them and then rolled the appropriate result on that spell's table.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.31
Scales of Mortality			KEY:Envoy of Balance ~ Scales of Mortality							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.EoBClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																													DESC:Once per day as a standard action, an envoy of balance can make a melee touch attack, delivering a killing touch against a living, non-neutral creature. If the attack hits, treat as a power word kill spell. If killled, its bodily remains (but not its equipment) turn to dust and the envoy of balance becomes aware of that creature's alignment. She may then touch the remains of another dead creature with an alignment opposite to, Hit Dice less than or equal to, the slain creature's. This revives the second dead creature as if via true resurrection. The envoy of balance can delay using this reviving touch for up to 1 hour after successfully using the killing touch.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.31

Aligned Annulment				KEY:Endowment ~ Aligned Annulment									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.EoBEndowment																						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Endowment ~ Aligned Counter																																																																				DESC:As a standard action, the envoy of balance can expend a spell with an alignment descriptor to automatically (without requiring a caster level check) dispel a spell with the opposite descriptor. The spell she expends must be of the same level or higher than the spell being dispelled.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.30
Aligned Counter				KEY:Endowment ~ Aligned Counter									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.EoBEndowment																																																																																																		DESC:The envoy of balance can counterspell a spell with an alignment descriptor using a spell with the opposite alignment descriptor. The spell used must be higher level than the spell being countered. If the envoy of balance has the Improved Counterspell feat the spell can be the same level or she counter as an immediate action with an appopriate spell at least 2 levels higher than the spell to be countered.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.30
Planar Parity				KEY:Endowment ~ Planar Parity										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.EoBEndowment																																																																																																		DESC:Protection from chaos/evil/IJood/law and similar effects no longer prevent bodily contact from creatures summoned by the envoy of balance. Neutral creatures summoned by the envoy of balance also gain the counterpoised simple creature template.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.31
Spiritual Equilibrium			KEY:Endowment ~ Spiritual Equilibrium								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.EoBEndowment																						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Versatile Channeler																																																																					DESC:The envoy of balance's class levels count as cleric levels for determining the effects of her channel energy ability. If she has the spontaneous casting class feature, she is no longer restricted to either cure or inflict spells. Each time the envoy of balance converts a spell, she can choose to convert it into a cure spell or an inflict spell. When using the Versatile Channeler feat, her effective cleric level is no longer reduced by 2-instead, she uses her full effective cleric level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.31
Twinned Channeling			KEY:Endowment ~ Twinned Channeling									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.EoBEndowment																						PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Endowment ~ Spiritual Equilibrium																																																																			DESC:When channeling energy, the envoy of balance can simultaneously release waves of positive and negative energy. She chooses a category of creatures (either living or undead), and this conjoined energy both heals and harms the affected creatures.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.31
Utterly Inscrutable			KEY:Endowment ~ Utterly Inscrutable									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.EoBEndowment																																																																																PREVARGTEQ:EoDLVL,8															DESC:The envoy of balance gains the benefits of a mind blank spell whose caster level is equal to her character level. She can suppress this ability as a swift action and resume it as an immediate action.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.31

# ==============================
# Ninja Tricks
# ==============================

Blood Debt					KEY:Ninja Trick ~ Blood Debt										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:NinjaClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.NinjaTrick.NinjaTrickOnly													VISIBLE:YES																																																																													DESC:A ninja with this ability gains In Harm's Way as a bonus feat, even if she doesn't meet the prerequisites. When the ninja intercepts an attack using this feat, she can spend 1 ki point to impose a blood debt on the aided ally. The ninja's ki pool is reduced by 1 until she ends this effect, which she may do as an immediate action. If the ninja ends the blood debt in response to a successful attack against her by a creature the indebted ally threatens, the ally (who must be willing) takes full damage from that attack and any associated effects instead of the ninja.																																																		ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|In Harm's Way																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.18
Kamikaze					KEY:Ninja Trick ~ Kamikaze										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:NinjaClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Supernatural.NinjaTrick.NinjaTrickOnly													VISIBLE:YES																																																																													DESC:A ninja with this ability strikes without concern for her own well-being. The ninja can spend 1 point from her ki pool to give her unarmed strikes and any weapons she wields the vicious weapon special ability for 1 round per level. The ninja can spend 1 ki point to dismiss this effect.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.18
Redirect Force				KEY:Ninja Trick ~ Redirect Force									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:NinjaClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.NinjaTrick.NinjaTrickOnly												VISIBLE:YES																																																																													DESC:If the ninja has a feat that allows her to attempt a combat maneuver without provoking attacks of opportunity, she can choose to provoke them anyway when she performs that maneuver. If she does so and takes damage from the attack of opportunity, the ninja adds the damage as a bonus on her attack roll instead of as a penalty.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.18
Kawarimi					KEY:Ninja Trick ~ Kawarimi										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:NinjaClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Supernatural.NinjaTrick.NinjaTrickOnly													VISIBLE:YES																PREMULT:1,[PREVARGTEQ:NinjaTrickLVL,10],[PREVARGTEQ:RogueTalentLVL,10]																																																		DESC:Once per day when a successful attack is made against a ninja with this ability, as an immediate action she can spend 1 ki point to attempt a Stealth check opposed by the attacker's Perception check. The ninja can attempt this check while being observed as long as she has cover or concealment (or an ability that allows her to attempt Stealth checks without cover or concealment). If she's successful, the opponent's attack hits an inanimate object that the attacker mistook for the ninja, and the ninja may move into an adjacent square and is hidden from the attacker.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGEp.:18

# ==============================
# Ranger Traps
# ==============================

Firework Trap				KEY:Ranger Trap ~ Firework Trap				SORTKEY:Trap Firework		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RangerClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.RangerTrap.Extraordinary.Supernatural																																																																																											DESC:You can only add this to a fire or smoke trap. The trap explodes in a flash of colored lights. All creatures within 10 feet must succeed at a saving throw (Fortitude if an extraordinary firework trap, Will if supernatural) or be blinded for 1d4+1 rounds.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Limning Trap				KEY:Ranger Trap ~ Limning Trap				SORTKEY:Trap Limning		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RangerClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.RangerTrap.Extraordinary.Supernatural																																																																																											DESC:This trap sprays glowing dust into the trapped square and all adjacent squares. A creature covered in this dust glows like a candle (becoming visibly outlined if invisible) and takes a -20 penalty on Stealth checks. The dust's effects last for 1 round per ranger level or until the creature washes it off (a move action requiring water or some other cleanser).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Smoke Trap					KEY:Ranger Trap ~ Smoke Trap					SORTKEY:Trap Smoke		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RangerClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.RangerTrap.Extraordinary.Supernatural																																																																																											DESC:This trap bellows out thick, choking smoke that fills the trapped square and all adjacent squares. Any breathing creature in these squares must succeed at a Fortitude saving throws or take a ?4 penalty to Strength and Dexterity every round it's within the smoke and for 1d4+1 rounds after leaving the smoke. All sight, even darkvision, is ineffective in or through the smoke. The smoke lasts for 1 round per 2 ranger levels, and is dispersed by wind as fog cloud.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Toxic Fumes Trap				KEY:Ranger Trap ~ Toxic Fumes Trap				SORTKEY:Toxic Fumes Smoke	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:RangerClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.RangerTrap.Extraordinary.Supernatural																																																																																											DESC:You can add this to a smoke trap. The smoke this trap creates is extremely noxious. Any breathing creature must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw (in addition to the Fortitude save for the smoke trap) or be nauseated every round it's within the smoke and for 1d4+1 rounds after leaving the smoke.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.25

