Impossible Bloodline			KEY:Sorcerer Bloodline ~ Impossible									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.ClassSpecialization.SorcererBloodline																																																																																														DESC:You can see beyond the mundane, and are capable of visualizing the improbable, and even the impossible.																																																																																																																															ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Impossible Bloodline ~ Bloodline Arcana|Impossible Bloodline ~ Bonus Spells|Impossible Bloodline ~ Disorienting Touch	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Impossible Bloodline ~ Spontaneous Generation|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,3|PREVARLT:BloodlineLVL,20	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|KEY:Impossible Bloodline ~ Distracting Pattern||PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,9	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Impossible Bloodline ~ Relativity|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,15	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Impossible Bloodline ~ Living Paradox|PREVARGTEQ:BloodlineLVL,20	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Impossible Bloodline Feat|BloodlineFeatCount																																																																																																																																																									CSKILL:Knowledge (Engineering)			SOURCEPAGE:p.21

